He has been in football for most of his life and has also played overseas. Now Tweeps pay tribute to him as one of the best strikers of all time. The 42-year-old is Bafana Bafana's top scorer of all time with 31 goals and he was recently the head coach of Cape Town City. Now the star's long-time supporters have taken to Twitter to pay tribute to the legend, giving him roses while he can still smell them.     